<!-- +++++++++++ mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area">
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> is a type of
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_area"/>.
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> contains information that is needed to determine the
	projection from some mechanical design model to a corresponding picture on a screen.
	The design model may be represented by any type of shape, such as a wireframe, surface, or solid.
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> is a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_area"/> 
	that is restricted to a certain presentation hierarchy.
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> shall be a singleâ€“window presentation of a product;
	no other 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_area">presentation_areas</express_ref> 
	shall be included in a <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b>.
	The model that is presented shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation:ir_express:aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation"/>. 
	The camera model used may provide light sources and hidden line and hidden surface removal.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR1 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area.wr:WR1">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	of a <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> shall only be 
	<express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement">axis2_placements</express_ref>
	or 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item">mapped_items</express_ref>. 
	In the latter case the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/> 
	of the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map"/> 
	that is the
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/>
	of such a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_view"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR2 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area.wr:WR2">
<p>
	The items of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_view"/>  
	shall only be 
	<express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement">axis2_placements</express_ref>
	or 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item">mapped_items</express_ref>. 
	In the latter case a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/>
	may be of type 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_image_3d_with_scale"/> 
	with the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/>
	of the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map"/>
	that is the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/>
	of such a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	being a 
	<express_ref linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation:ir_express:aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation"/>. 
	If the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	is not a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_image_3d_with_scale"/>, 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/> 
	of the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map"/> 
	that is the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/>
	of this 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	shall be a different 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_view"/>.
</p>
	<note>
		If a user of this part of ISO 10303 includes in addition to 
		<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_image_3d_with_scale"/> 
		other subtypes of 
		<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/>
		into a schema, additional rules may be required to exclude these subtypes to be instantiated in a
		<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_view"/>. 
		This part of ISO 10303 does not hinder the instantiation of subtypes of 
		<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/>
		that are not specified in this part.
	</note>
</ext_description>

<!-- WR3 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area.wr:WR3">
	The rectangular size of the <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> shall be specified by positive values. 
	The same shall be valid for the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_set"/> 
	that this area is enclosed in.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR4 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area.wr:WR4">
	The drawing space of a <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area</b> shall be specified in a
	2D co-ordinate system.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR5 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area.wr:WR5">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_usage.mapping_origin"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_usage"/> 
	that is the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/>  
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_image_3d_with_scale"/> 
	within a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.presentation_view"/> 
	shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_model_d3"/>, 
	a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_model_d3_with_hlhsr"/>, 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_model_with_light_sources"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation">
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b> is a type of
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/>.
	A <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b> specifies the shape and optionally related
	presentation styles that shall be viewed in a 
	<express_ref linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation:ir_express:aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_area"/>.
	All 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	of a <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b> shall be either 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item">styled_items</express_ref> 
	that describe shape, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_model_d3">camera_model_d3s</express_ref>, 
	or 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item">mapped_items</express_ref>.
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item">Mapped_items</express_ref> 
	shall be mappings of either 
	<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation">shape_representations</express_ref> 
	or of other <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b>s.
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item.item"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	may either reference directly a
	<express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.geometric_representation_item"/> 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="topology_schema:ir_express:topology_schema.topological_representation_item"/>, 
	or indirectly via a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	that is the mapping of a 
	<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/>.
	The use of styles and style attributes for points, curves, and surfaces is restricted.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR1 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR1">
	Each entity in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/>, 
	a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/>, 
	an 
	<express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement"/>, 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_organization_schema:ir_express:presentation_organization_schema.camera_model_d3"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR2 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR2">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/> 
	of the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map"/> 
	that is the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/> 
	of a
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	in a <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b> shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/>
	or another <b>mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation</b>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR3 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR3">
	The item of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	may be a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	only, if the 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> 
	has a 
	<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> 
	as its 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR4 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR4">
	Each item in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment.styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment"/> 
	that is referenced by a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	shall 
	be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.point_style"/>,
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>, 
	or 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_usage"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR5 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR5">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_by_context.style_context"/> 
	attribute of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_by_context"/> 
	shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/>
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR6 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR6">
	For each 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.point_style"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment.styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment"/> 
	that is referenced 	by a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.point_style.marker_colour"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.point_style.marker_size"/> 
	attribute shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.positive_length_measure"/>; 
	the
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.point_style.marker"/>  
	attribute shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.marker_type"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR7 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR7">
	For each 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment.styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment"/> 
	that is referenced by a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_colour"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_width"/> 
	attribute shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.positive_length_measure"/>;
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_font"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font"/> 
	or a
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.draughting_pre_defined_curve_font"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR8 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR8">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_usage.style"/> 
	attribute of each 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_usage"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment.styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.presentation_style_assignment"/> 
	that is referenced by a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.styled_item"/> 
	in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation.items"/> 
	shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_side_style"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR9 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR9">
	Each item in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_side_style.styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_side_style"/> 
	shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_parameter_line"/>, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_control_grid"/>, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_silhouette"/>, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_segmentation_curve"/>, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_boundary"/>, 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_fill_area"/>, 
	or 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_rendering"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR 10-->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR10">
	Each item in the set of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.fill_area_style.fill_styles"/> 
	of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.fill_area_style"/> 
	shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.fill_area_style_colour"/>, 
	and the
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.fill_area_style_colour.fill_colour"/> 
	attribute of the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.fill_area_style_colour"/> 
	shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR11 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR11">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_parameter_line.style_of_parameter_lines"/> 
	attribute of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_parameter_line"/> 
	shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_rendering"/> 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>. 
	In the case of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/> 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_colour"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_width"/> 
	attribute shall be a 
	<express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.positive_length_measure"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_font"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font"/> 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.draughting_pre_defined_curve_font"/>. 
	In the case of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_rendering"/> 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_rendering_properties.rendered_colour"/> 
	attribute of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_rendering.rendering_properties"/> 
	shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR12 -->
<ext_description linkend="aic_mechanical_design_shaded_presentation.mechanical_design_shaded_presentation_representation.wr:WR12">
	The 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_control_grid.style_of_control_grid"/> 
	attribute of a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.surface_style_control_grid"/> 
	shall be a
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_rendering"/> 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>. 
	In the case of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/> 
	the
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_colour"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.colour_rgb"/>  
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.draughting_pre_defined_colour"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_width"/> 
	attribute shall be a
	<express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.positive_length_measure"/>; 
	the 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style.curve_font"/> 
	attribute shall be either a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font"/> 
	or a 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.draughting_pre_defined_curve_font"/>. 
	In the case of 
	<express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_rendering"/> 
	the 
